criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Childhood obesity (>97 percentile WHO references)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  being involved in any weight control, physical activity, behavior therapy, or gastric
             surgery program;

          -  familial history of dyslipidemia or essential hypertension;

          -  medications or hormones, which may influence cardiovascular function, body
             composition, lipid or glucose metabolism in the preceding 6 months;

          -  orthopaedic affection limiting physical activity;

          -  genetic disorder or another chronic disease;
